When I open popup to see table infos of table with Name "jit014"
When I update popup with textbox Name "Table name" to value "jit014dup"
When I press Save button modal popup without wait
Then I should see inline error message of textbox label "Table name" has value "Table name already exist"
When I click delete button of table when table popup open
